  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    FlowingTextResolution
    sets resolution of flowing text, possible values: LOW, MEDIUM, HIGH
    FontStyle
    sets style of flowing text, possible values: Plain, Bold, Italic, ItalicBold
    FontType
    sets font of flowing text, possible values: Arial, Courier, Georgia, Serif
    frameStyle
    sets style of frame, possible values: Thin, Normal, Bold
    pointShape
    sets point shape, possible values: FullPoint, Circle, Square, Triangle, Diamond
    showNet
    allows to decide to show net (Yes / No)
